Sure. It's a real job.

184
00:13:54,765 --> 00:13:57,768
而不是为了让梅维开心 你赖着不走的低廉借口
Not a cheap excuse to keep Mavis happy, so you never leave here.

185
00:13:57,835 --> 00:14:00,404
没错 所以 我在想
Right. So, I was thinking,

186
00:14:00,471 --> 00:14:04,441
既然我们都有这么多人类来这儿了 那或许可以更新一些配备
since we have so many humans now, maybe update some of the acts?

187
00:14:04,508 --> 00:14:05,910
比如 或许换一下魔术师
Like, maybe the magician?

188
00:14:05,976 --> 00:14:07,978
三只眼哈利有什么不好
What's wrong with Harry Three-Eye?

189
00:14:08,045 --> 00:14:11,182
对于人类来说 他可能有点老派
Well, he might be a little old-school for the humans.

190
00:14:11,248 --> 00:14:13,250
告诉我 先生 你的牌是什么
Tell me, sir, what was your card?

191
00:14:13,317 --> 00:14:14,785
黑桃三
The three of spades?

192
00:14:16,754 --> 00:14:18,956
这是你的牌吗 我的朋友
Is this your card, my friend?

193
00:14:19,723 --> 00:14:20,891
哇哦
Whoa!

194
00:14:22,860 --> 00:14:24,662
不行 哈利很棒
No, Harry's great.

195
00:14:24,728 --> 00:14:26,864
不能把观众不嗨怪在哈利头上
Can't blame Harry for the crowd not being hip.

196
00:14:26,931 --> 00:14:29,033
