Okay, what about Wayne?

197
00:14:29,099 --> 00:14:30,701
韦恩 你是疯了吗 他是我的兄弟
Wayne? Are you nuts? He's my boy.

198
00:14:30,768 --> 00:14:32,670
那能换个活儿给他吗 不要网球可以吗
Then maybe something other than tennis?

199
00:14:32,736 --> 00:14:34,872
好了 你要做的就是
Okay, so, what you wanna do

200
00:14:34,939 --> 00:14:36,807
球来的时候举起拍子
is lift the racket right on impact,

201
00:14:36,808 --> 00:14:38,409
然后就能打出一手好球了
so you get that nice top spin.

202
00:14:38,476 --> 00:14:39,944
试试打一个吧
Try and hit one.

203
00:14:48,786 --> 00:14:51,722
什么东西 什么声音 是从我身上发出来的
What is that? What's the noise? It's on me!

204
00:14:51,789 --> 00:14:53,691
是我给你买的手机响了而已
It's just the cell phone I got you.

205
00:14:53,757 --> 00:14:54,803
克利夫顿在给你发短信
Clifton's sending you a

206
00:14:54,804 --> 00:14:56,760
好让你能练习下怎么回短信
text so you can practice how to write back.

207
00:15:00,798 --> 00:15:01,999
什么东 这破手机不听使唤
What the... It's not doing it.

208
00:15:02,066 --> 00:15:03,100
我来
I got it.

209
00:15:08,606 --> 00:15:09,707
现在你可以给克利夫顿发短信了
Now you can text Clifton.

210
00:15:10,708 --> 00:15:12,009
好吧好吧
All right, fine.

211
00:15:13,310 --> 00:15:14,778
你是怎么做到的
How do you do this?

212
00:15:14,845 --> 00:15:15,965
或许是你的指甲的问题
Maybe it's your fingernails.

213
00:15:16,013 --> 00:15:18,415
很简单的 看 我给梅维丝发条短信
It's easy. Look. I'll text Mavis.

214
00:15:18,482 --> 00:15:21,352
今晚要约会了 好激动啊
Psyched for date night.

215
00:15:21,418 --> 00:15:23,687
看见么 看 她立马就回我了
See? And now look, she texted right back.

216
00:15:23,754 --> 00:15:25,890
“取消吧 我离不开丹尼斯”
Gotta cancel. Can't leave Dennis.

217
00:15:26,490 --> 00:15:27,825
好吧
Okay.

218
00:15:27,892 --> 00:15:32,563
我们再也不能独处了吗
Are we never allowed to be alone again?

219
00:15:32,630 --> 00:15:36,433
我也需要被爱啊
I need to feel loved, too.

220
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:39,236
然后发送
And send.

221
00:15:39,303 --> 00:15:42,573
够了 我只学会一件事 你真窝囊
Okay. All that taught me is that you're pathetic.

222
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:44,875
嗯 知道了 或许你就用蓝牙
Yeah, got it. Maybe you should just get Bluetooth.

223
00:15:44,942 --> 00:15:47,244
没问题 蓝牙 过来
Okay. Blue Tooth, come over here.

224
00:15:50,314 --> 00:15:51,615
然后呢
So, now what?

225
00:15:56,086 --> 00:15:58,389
该起床啦 我的丹尼索维奇
Rise and shine, my Denisovich.

226
00:15:58,455 --> 00:16:00,157
嗨 外公
Hi, Papa.

227
00:16:00,224 --> 00:16:03,561
你好啊 我的小恶魔 你做了个香甜的噩梦吗
Hello, my little devil. Did you have sweet nightmares?

228
00:16:03,627 --> 00:16:07,431
嗯哼 我梦见了一条剑龙
Uh-huh. I dreamed that I saw a stegosaurus.

229
00:16:07,498 --> 00:16:09,667
噢 然后你在喝他的血吗
Oh... And were you drinking his blood?

230
00:16:10,301 --> 00:16:11,635
没有
No.

231
00:16:11,702 --> 00:16:12,970
那不管他了
Just throwing it out there.

232
00:16:13,037 --> 00:16:14,505
嘿 想不想做些很酷的事
Hey! You want to do something cool?

233
00:16:14,571 --> 00:16:17,141
想
Yeah!

234
00:16:17,207 --> 00:16:21,745
我来教你怎样变成蝙蝠 像我一样
I'm going to teach you how to turn into a bat. Like me.

235
00:16:21,812 --> 00:16:23,647
-看见没 -好酷
- See? - Cool.

236
00:16:23,714 --> 00:16:25,349
没错 很酷 我就说了
Yes! Cool, like I said.

237
00:16:26,183 --> 00:16:27,318
现在你试试
Now you try.

238
00:16:28,218 --> 00:16:29,820
我是只蝙蝠
I'm a bat.

239
00:16:29,887 --> 00:16:31,755
我是只蝙蝠 我是只蝙蝠 我是只蝙蝠
I'm a bat. I'm a bat. I'm a bat.

240
00:16:31,822 --> 00:16:32,957
我是只蝙蝠
I'm a bat.

241
00:16:33,724 --> 00:16:35,292
我的意思是 一只真正的蝙蝠
I mean, a real bat.

242
00:16:35,359 --> 00:16:36,827
我是只蝙蝠
I'm a bat!

243
00:16:38,762 --> 00:16:43,267
丹尼索维奇 深呼吸 你真的可以变成蝙蝠的
Denisovich. Take a breath. You can really turn into a bat.

244
00:16:43,334 --> 00:16:45,369
试试 找到蝙蝠的感觉
Try. Feel the bat.

245
00:16:47,738 --> 00:16:49,239
不是只小鸡
Not a chicken.

246
00:16:51,709 --> 00:16:53,744
那是什么 机械舞吗
What's that? The electric boogaloo?

247
00:16:53,811 --> 00:16:56,680
我要是跳段舞给你看 你能试着飞一下吗
If I show you I can bust a move, will you try to fly, then?

248
00:16:56,747 --> 00:16:57,747
嗯哼
Uh-huh.

249
00:17:12,627 --> 00:17:14,431
爸爸 你们怎么在跳舞
Dad? Why are you guys dancing?

250
00:17:15,598 --> 00:17:17,800
呃 他在梦舞
Uh, he was sleep-dancing.

251
00:17:17,867 --> 00:17:19,236
过来 小甜心 回床上睡觉吧
Come on, sweetie. Back to bed.

252
00:17:19,303 --> 00:17:22,239
“回床上睡觉吧” 已经过了晚上八点了
Back to bed? It's already after 8:00 p.M.

253
00:17:22,306 --> 00:17:24,241
你不记得新的作息表了吗
Don't you remember the new sleep schedule?

254
00:17:24,308 --> 00:17:25,209
他要去上半天的人类课堂
He's going to human classes half the day.

255
00:17:27,111 --> 00:17:28,675
今晚他要是能睡到凌晨两点的话
If he could just sleep till 2:00 A.M.

256
00:17:28,676 --> 00:17:30,114
对他来说就太好了
Tonight, it'd be so great for him.

257
00:17:30,180 --> 00:17:32,116
但是 宝贝小死神 韦恩的六条小狼犬
But, honeydeath, six of Wayne's wolf pups

258
