今晚要开生日派对啊
are having a birthday party tonight.

259
00:17:34,184 --> 00:17:36,286
你不会忍心让他错过吧
You wouldn't want him to miss that.

260
00:17:36,353 --> 00:17:37,794
爸爸 我爱那些小狼犬
Dad, I love the wolf pups,

261
00:17:37,795 --> 00:17:40,124
但是他们对于丹尼斯来说 有些太粗暴了
but they're a little too rough for Dennis.

262
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:42,426
“太粗暴”
Too rough?

263
00:17:42,493 --> 00:17:44,495
你没注意到吗 丹尼斯不一样
Haven't you noticed? Dennis is different.

264
00:17:44,561 --> 00:17:47,364
你在说什么 丹尼索维奇不该与怪兽为伍吗
What are you saying? Denisovich shouldn't be around monsters?

265
00:17:47,431 --> 00:17:50,668
-我爱怪兽 动画片 动画片 -哈
I love monsters! Video! Video! Ha!

266
00:17:50,734 --> 00:17:52,836
噢 你是想要让德古拉外公看看你的怪兽动画片吗
Oh, you wanna show Papa Drac your monster video?

267
00:17:52,903 --> 00:17:53,903
没错
Yeah!

268
00:17:56,774 --> 00:17:58,909
谁是最酷的怪兽
Who's the coolest monster?

269
00:17:58,976 --> 00:18:00,744
蛋糕糕
Kakie!

270
00:18:00,811 --> 00:18:03,781
蛋糕糕是一只快乐的怪兽
Wee! Kakie one happy monster!

271
00:18:03,847 --> 00:18:06,383
蛋糕糕爱吃蛋糕 好吃
Kakie love cake! Yummy!

272
00:18:06,450 --> 00:18:08,786
汤米肚子痛了
Tummy get a tummyache.

273
00:18:08,852 --> 00:18:12,222
哇哦 哇哦 哇哦 那根本不是只怪兽
Whoa, whoa, whoa. How is that a monster?

274
00:18:12,289 --> 00:18:14,391
吃点蛋糕吧 唔兹拉帕巴姆
Have some cake, Wuzzlelumplebum.

275
00:18:14,458 --> 00:18:18,362
记住了 孩子们 真正的怪兽喜欢分享
Remember, kids, a real monster always shares.

276
00:18:18,429 --> 00:18:23,233
“分享”没错 我一想到怪兽的时候就会想到“分享”
Shares? Yes! When I think monsters, I think "Shares."

277
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:26,804
现在 让我来告诉你什么才是真正的怪兽 丹尼索维奇
Now, let me tell you what a real monster is, Denisovich.

278
00:18:26,870 --> 00:18:30,474
爸爸 别这样 他才五岁啊 别逼他
Dad, please. He's practically five already. Don't force it.

279
00:18:34,344 --> 00:18:36,580
慢慢来 唔兹拉帕巴姆
Slow down, Wuzzlelumplebum.

