00:18:42,052 --> 00:18:45,622
一闪一闪小星星 究竟何物
# Twinkle, twinkle, little star How I wonder #

281
00:18:45,689 --> 00:18:48,158
妈咪 我已经过了听摇篮曲的年龄了
Mommy, I'm too old for lullabies.

282
00:18:48,225 --> 00:18:50,394
什么 摇篮曲不是那样唱的
What? That's not how that one goes.

283
00:18:50,461 --> 00:18:52,029
大多数人都这样唱
This is the way most people sing it.

284
00:18:52,096 --> 00:18:54,298
“大多数人” 我的版本又怎么了
Most people? What's wrong with...

