00:18:54,364 --> 00:18:57,801
受苦 受难 痛苦中尖叫
# Suffer, suffer, scream in pain #

286
00:18:57,868 --> 00:19:01,238
鲜血从你脑中溢
# Blood is spilling from your brain #

287
00:19:01,305 --> 00:19:04,007
-爸爸 -得了吧 你知道我就是这样唱给你听的
Daddy. Come on. You know how I sang it to you.

288
00:19:04,074 --> 00:19:07,211
僵尸咬你像葡干
# Zombies gnaw you like a plum #

289
00:19:07,277 --> 00:19:10,414
撕成碎片你完蛋
# Piercing cries and you succumb #

290
00:19:12,049 --> 00:19:15,953
