00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,855
伍皮 伟伦 维皮还有韦恩
Whoopi, Waylon, Weepy and Wanye.

295
00:19:53,557 --> 00:19:56,160
丹尼索维奇 好孩子 你来了
Denisovich! My big boy! You made it!

296
00:19:57,161 --> 00:19:59,396
我仔细想了下你所说的 爸爸
I thought about what you said, Dad.

297
00:19:59,463 --> 00:20:01,198
或许我有点保护过度了
Maybe I was being a little overprotective.

298
00:20:01,265 --> 00:20:03,167
谢谢你 棺材蛋糕小甜心
Thank you, coffin cake.

299
00:20:04,168 --> 00:20:05,803
丹尼斯 我爱你 噌
Dennis! I love you! Zing!

300
00:20:05,869 --> 00:20:07,404
嗨 温妮
Hi, Winnie.

301
00:20:07,471 --> 00:20:10,607
我真的好爱你的美味草莓锁 噌 噌
I just love your yummy strawberry locks! Zing, zing!

302
00:20:13,777 --> 00:20:17,648
温妮 别老缠着丹尼斯 亲爱的 抱歉 梅维丝
Winnie. Give him his space, hon. I'm sorry, Mavis.

303
00:20:17,714 --> 00:20:20,384
没事的 旺达阿姨 他们只是在闹着玩
It's okay, Aunt Wanda. They're just playing.

304
00:20:20,450 --> 00:20:24,154
噢 天呐 地狱边境吗 我之前爱死那游戏了
Holy rabies! Limbo? I used to love that game!

305
00:20:24,221 --> 00:20:26,056
去玩啊 梅维
Get in there, Mavey.

306
00:20:26,123 --> 00:20:27,724
真的吗 但是我现在为人母了啊
Really? But I'm a parent now.

307
00:20:27,791 --> 00:20:29,159
给他们看看是怎么玩
Show 'em how it's done.

308
00:20:29,226 --> 00:20:30,460
好的 好的 好的
Okay. Okay, okay.

309
00:20:39,469 --> 00:20:41,071
不是吧 一个皮纳塔
No way! A pinata?

310
00:20:44,942 --> 00:20:46,677
噢 梅维丝 亲爱的 那个稍后再玩
Oh, Mavis, honey. That's for later.

311
00:20:48,712 --> 00:20:50,352
我们不想小狼犬们吃太多的
We don't want the pups to have too much...

312
00:20:50,814 --> 00:20:52,249
糖果
Candy!

313
00:20:55,852 --> 00:20:56,852
糖
Sugar.

314
00:21:04,561 --> 00:21:06,597
对不起 是我引起的吗
I'm sorry. Did I start all that?

315
00:21:06,663 --> 00:21:08,703
别担心 幼崽们就是这样闹腾
Don't worry. There's a reason they call it a litter.

316
00:21:20,844 --> 00:21:22,813
丹尼斯 你还好吗
Dennis! Are you okay?

317
00:21:22,879 --> 00:21:24,781
我抢到一颗糖
I got a candy.

318
00:21:24,848 --> 00:21:26,750
看 你掉了颗牙
Look! Your tooth came out.

319
00:21:26,817 --> 00:21:29,253
不是吧 他的牙磕掉了吗
Are you kidding me? He got his tooth knocked out?

320
00:21:29,319 --> 00:21:32,356
噢 是的 没错 要长出尖牙啦
Oh, yes, indeed. Here comes the fang.

321
00:21:32,422 --> 00:21:35,525
爸爸 他的乳齿都不是尖牙 这颗怎么会是呢
Dad. His baby tooth wasn't a fang. Why would this one be?

322
00:21:35,592 --> 00:21:37,160
他不是个怪物
He's not a monster.

323
00:21:42,099 --> 00:21:45,135
太阳就要出来了 我们得送他去上课了
The sun's gonna come out soon, and we gotta get to his classes.

324
00:21:45,202 --> 00:21:48,939
我们这的课程有什么不好吗 比如说儿童瑜伽
What's wrong with the classes we have here? Like the kids' yoga?

325
00:21:49,006 --> 00:21:53,043
瑜伽
Yoga!

326
00:21:53,110 --> 00:21:55,178
这儿是丹尼索维奇的家
This is Denisovich's home.

327
00:21:55,245 --> 00:21:56,780
我不知道 爸爸
I don't know, Dad.

328
00:21:56,847 --> 00:21:58,215
你不知道什么
What don't you know?

329
00:21:58,282 --> 00:22:01,752
嗯 我们在想要不要搬家
Well, we've been talking about moving.

330
00:22:01,818 --> 00:22:04,254
搬到对于丹尼斯来说更安全的地方去
Somewhere safer for Dennis.

331
00:22:04,321 --> 00:22:07,224
或许搬到加利福尼亚 强尼长大的地方去
Maybe where Johnny grew up in California.

332
00:22:07,291 --> 00:22:08,719
对不起 但是你不能
I'm sorry, but you can't

333
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:11,161
强迫别人变成自身以外的东西
just make somebody something they're not.

334
00:22:13,297 --> 00:22:14,765
过来 亲爱的 我们得走了
Come on, honey. We have to go.

335
00:22:14,831 --> 00:22:16,033
噌 噌
Zing, zing?

336
00:22:17,167 --> 00:22:19,970
梅维 等等 你不是认真的吧
Mavey, wait. You can't mean that.

337
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:25,242
这事儿你有份吗 要搬家
You're in on this? The leaving?

338
00:22:25,309 --> 00:22:28,145
呃 都还不确定
Uh... It's not definite at all.

339
00:22:28,211 --> 00:22:29,413
她只是在说说而已
It's just something she's definitely talking about,

340
00:22:29,479 --> 00:22:31,715
